Package org.intermine.api.query

Class MemoryQueryStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.intermine.api.query.MemoryQueryStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QueryStore
    public class MemoryQueryStore
extends java.lang.Object
implements QueryStore
    An in-memory implementation of a query store. This implementation is aware of when it was instantiated, and complains differently to the user about missing keys depending on whether the key is from a time before the lifetime of this object, in which case the server may have been restarted, or after, in which case it is all their fault.
    Author:
    Alex Kalderimis
